<h2 id="table-삭제하기">Table 삭제하기</h2>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">DROP</span> <span class="n">TABLE</span> <span class="n">IF</span> <span class="n">EXISTS</span> <span class="n">tbname</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>IF EXISTS는 옵션이다.</li>
</ul>

