<h2 id="table-수정하기">Table 수정하기</h2>

<h3 id="새로운-컬럼-추가">새로운 컬럼 추가</h3>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">ALTER</span> <span class="n">TABLE</span> <span class="n">colname</span> <span class="n">ADD</span> <span class="n">COLUMN</span> <span class="n">new</span> <span class="n">colname</span> <span class="n">col</span> <span class="n">option</span><span class="p">;</span>


<span class="n">ex</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">ALTER</span> <span class="n">TABLE</span> <span class="n">profile</span> <span class="n">ADD</span> <span class="n">COLUMN</span> <span class="n">height</span> <span class="n">INT</span> <span class="n">NOT</span> <span class="n">NULL</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="/assets/img/back_end/2020_01_09/new_col.png" alt="new_col" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>height라는 칼럼이 추가된 것을 확인할 수 있다.</li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h3 id="컬럼-구조-수정">컬럼 구조 수정</h3>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">ALTER</span> <span class="n">TABLE</span> <span class="n">tbname</span> <span class="n">MODIFY</span> <span class="n">COLUMN</span> <span class="n">colname</span> <span class="n">col</span> <span class="n">option</span><span class="p">;</span>


<span class="n">ex</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">ALTER</span> <span class="n">TABLE</span> <span class="n">Profile</span> <span class="n">MODIFY</span> <span class="n">COLUMN</span> <span class="n">pID</span> <span class="n">INT</span> <span class="n">NOT</span> <span class="n">NULL</span> <span class="n">PRIMARY</span> <span class="n">KEY</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="/assets/img/back_end/2020_01_09/modify_col.png" alt="modify_col" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>pID 컬럼에 Key에 PRI 즉 pID값이 Primary key로 수정된것을 확인할 수 있다.</li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h3 id="컬럼-삭제">컬럼 삭제</h3>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">ALTER</span> <span class="n">TABLE</span> <span class="n">tbname</span> <span class="n">DROP</span> <span class="n">COLUMN</span> <span class="n">colname</span><span class="p">;</span>


<span class="n">ex</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">ALTER</span> <span class="n">TABLE</span> <span class="n">Profile</span> <span class="n">DROP</span> <span class="n">COLUMN</span> <span class="n">height</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="/assets/img/back_end/2020_01_09/del_col.png" alt="del_col" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>height 컬럼이 삭제된 것을 확인할 수 있다.</li>
</ul>

<p><br /><br /></p>

<h2 id="table-초기화">Table 초기화</h2>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">TRUNCATE</span> <span class="n">TABLE</span> <span class="n">tbname</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="n">ex</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">TRUNCATE</span> <span class="n">TABLE</span> <span class="n">profile</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>테이블 설정(정의)는 남겨놓고 모든 데이터를 삭제하는 명령어 입니다.</li>
</ul>

